OL,3,CWho's who in the new Plaid Cymru
OL,4,Cgovernment?
OL,6,FFirst Minister Rhun ap Iorwerth has
OL,7,Fannounced the new Welsh Government
OL,8,FCabinet.
OL,10,FThe Plaid Cymru leader was elected as
OL,11,Fleader of the country by Members of
OL,12,Fthe Senedd (MSs) on Tuesday, making
OL,13,Fhim the first politician not from
OL,14,FLabour to hold the office.
OL,16,FHe succeeds Eluned Morgan, who lost
OL,17,Fher seat in the Senedd election last
OL,18,Fweek and subsequently resigned as
OL,19,FWelsh Labour leader after a
OL,20,Fdevastating set of results for the
OL,21,Fparty.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
