OL,3,CWho's who in the new Plaid Cymru
OL,4,Cgovernment?
OL,6,FAfter the vote in the Senedd, the
OL,7,FPlaid Cymru leader was sworn in at the
OL,8,FWelsh Government's HQ in Cathays Park.
OL,10,FAnnouncing the Ministerial team, Mr ap
OL,11,FIorwerth said: "I am confident that
OL,12,Fthis Cabinet will bring new energy,
OL,13,Fnew ideas, and a new direction to the
OL,14,Fleadership of our nation.
OL,16,F"The Cabinet will begin immediately
OL,17,Fthe task of creating a fairer, greener
OL,18,Fand more prosperous Wales for everyone
OL,19,Fwho lives here, whatever their
OL,20,Fcircumstances."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
