OL,3,CWho's who in the new Plaid Cymru
OL,4,Cgovernment?
OL,6,FThe details of the new Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment cabinet are below:
OL,9,FDeputy First Minister and Cabinet
OL,10,FMinister for Social Justice and
OL,11,FEquality ` Sioned Williams.
OL,13,FCabinet Minister for Finance ` Elin
OL,14,FJones.
OL,16,FTrefnydd, Chief Whip and Cabinet
OL,17,FMinister for Culture and Sport `
OL,18,FHeledd Fychan.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
