OL,6,FCabinet Minister for Government
OL,7,FEffectiveness and the Constitution `
OL,8,FDafydd Trystan Davies.
OL,10,FCabinet Minister for Health and Care `
OL,11,FMabon ap Gwynfor.
OL,13,FCabinet Minister for Enterprise,
OL,14,FConnectivity and Energy ` Adam Price.
OL,16,FCabinet Minister for Education and the
OL,17,FWelsh Language ` Anna Brychan.
OL,19,FCabinet Minister for Rural Resilience
OL,20,Fand Sustainability ` Llyr Gruffydd.
